halfway down.<br>
<br>
but the math explaination is that if you kill someone your lvl, you get 100 point.  there is a 5 pt reward/penalty after that for lvl difference.  therefore, if you kill someone 10 lvls below you , you only get 50 points.  when you kill someone more than 20 lvls below you, you get negative points.<br>
<br>
&lt;edit&gt;<br>
